ygData.messageBody:
FP far meh? level 6 more than enough to travel there. Just bank
everything and sprint to BB and take the boot to FP. The whole journey
is pretty much Mob free, my bard made it to FP at level 5-6 I think.

And nope, I don't get on Kali much. My nick there is Garford anyway. I
use Sereph ONLY for RPG games

[Useless fact of the day: I never ever played a male character in an RPG
game(be it PnP ones or electronic ones), unless I have no choice in the
gender and the 2 most used names are Sabella and Sereph in that order]

And hell no, I'm not a castration fanatic. I only castrated Enteri as it
took him so long to do a task for me and some people I dislike in not so
real life.

Always remember this fact: Sereph is a female name.

Sereph, door to door parang saleswoman who won't take no for an answer.
